The '''Enel Corugea Wind Farm''' is a wind power project in [[Tulcea County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 35 [[Vestas V90-2MW|Vestas V90]]  [[wind turbine]]s with a nominal output of 2 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 70 MW of power. Construction started in May 2011.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://energie.businesslive.ro/enel-construieste-un-parc-eolian-de-70-mw-in-judetul-tulcea/|title=Enel construieste un parc eolian de 70 MW in judetul Tulcea|date=2011-05-03|work=|publisher=''Energie Live''|language=Romanian|accessdate=2012-12-16}}</ref>

