'''Ricinelaidic acid''' or '''(+)-(''R'')-ricinelaidic acid''' is an [[saturation (chemistry)|unsaturated]] [[omega-9 fatty acid|omega-9]] [[trans fat|trans fatty acid]].  It is the [[Cis-trans isomerism|trans-isomer]] of the [[fatty acid]] [[ricinoleic acid]].

